    <string name="news_jurassic_title">Jurassic World Rebirth starts a new dinosaur-era story</string>
    <string name="news_jurassic_body">Jurassic World Rebirth is directed by Gareth Edwards and features Scarlett Johansson, Mahershala Ali, and Jonathan Bailey. Universal released the movie in July 2025 as a fresh story in the Jurassic franchise.</string>
